Romania’s Hidroelectrica to Secure EU110 Million EBRD Loan

-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 
2011-07-11T15:14:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/romania-s-hidroelectrica-to-secure-eu110-million-ebrd-loan.html
Romania ’s hydropower generator,
Hidroelectrica SA will sign an agreement tomorrow for a 110
million euro ($154 million) loan from the European Bank for
Reconstruction and Development, the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  The money will be used to fund the upgrade of one of its
hydropower plants, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez in Prague at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  